  1Ôćĺ# Type definitions for coding agent CLIs in SDK mode
  2Ôćĺ
  3ÔćĺFour major coding agent CLIs now offer programmatic access through TypeScript SDKs with well-defined type systems. **OpenCode provides the most complete formal specification** with a published OpenAPI 3.1.1 schema, while Claude Code and Codex offer comprehensive TypeScript types through npm packages. All four tools use similar patterns: streaming events via JSON lines, discriminated union types for messages, and structured configuration schemas.
  4Ôćĺ
  5Ôćĺ## Codex CLI has TypeScript SDK but no formal schema
  6Ôćĺ
  7ÔćĺOpenAI's Codex CLI provides programmatic control through the **`@openai/codex-sdk`** package, which wraps the bundled binary and exchanges JSONL events over stdin/stdout. Types are well-defined in source code but not published as JSON Schema or OpenAPI specifications.
  8Ôćĺ
  9Ôćĺ**Core SDK types from `@openai/codex-sdk`:**
 10Ôćĺ
 11Ôćĺ```typescript
 12Ôćĺinterface CodexOptions {
 13Ôćĺ  codexPathOverride?: string;
 14Ôćĺ  baseURL?: string;
 15Ôćĺ  apiKey?: string;
 16Ôćĺ  env?: Record<string, string>;
 17Ôćĺ}
 18Ôćĺ
 19Ôćĺinterface ThreadOptions {
 20Ôćĺ  model?: string;
 21Ôćĺ  sandboxMode?: "read-only" | "workspace-write" | "danger-full-access";
 22Ôćĺ  workingDirectory?: string;
 23Ôćĺ  skipGitRepoCheck?: boolean;
 24Ôćĺ}
 25Ôćĺ
 26Ôćĺinterface TurnOptions {
 27Ôćĺ  outputSchema?: Record<string, unknown>;  // JSON Schema for structured output
 28Ôćĺ}
 29Ôćĺ
 30Ôćĺtype Input = string | UserInput[];
 31Ôćĺinterface UserInput {
 32Ôćĺ  type: "text" | "local_image";
 33Ôćĺ  text?: string;
 34Ôćĺ  path?: string;
 35Ôćĺ}
 36Ôćĺ```
 37Ôćĺ
 38Ôćĺ**Event types for streaming (`runStreamed()`):**
 39Ôćĺ
 40Ôćĺ```typescript
 41Ôćĺtype EventType = "thread.started" | "turn.started" | "turn.completed" | 
 42Ôćĺ                 "turn.failed" | "item.started" | "item.updated" | 
 43Ôćĺ                 "item.completed" | "error";
 44Ôćĺ
 45Ôćĺinterface ThreadEvent {
 46Ôćĺ  type: EventType;
 47Ôćĺ  thread_id?: string;
 48Ôćĺ  usage?: { input_tokens: number; cached_input_tokens: number; output_tokens: number };
 49Ôćĺ  error?: { message: string };
 50Ôćĺ  item?: ThreadItem;
 51Ôćĺ}
 52Ôćĺ
 53Ôćĺtype ItemType = "agent_message" | "reasoning" | "command_execution" | 
 54Ôćĺ                "file_change" | "mcp_tool_call" | "web_search" | 
 55Ôćĺ                "todo_list" | "error" | "unknown";
 56Ôćĺ```
 57Ôćĺ
 58Ôćĺ**Key source files:** `sdk/typescript/src/` contains `items.ts`, `events.ts`, `options.ts`, `input.ts`, and `thread.ts`. Documentation at https://developers.openai.com/codex/sdk/ and https://developers.openai.com/codex/noninteractive/.
 59Ôćĺ
