 61Ôćĺ
 62Ôćĺ## Claude Code SDK offers the most comprehensive TypeScript types
 63Ôćĺ
 64ÔćĺNow rebranded as the **Claude Agent SDK**, the official package `@anthropic-ai/claude-agent-sdk` provides production-ready types with full coverage of tools, hooks, permissions, and streaming events.
 65Ôćĺ
 66Ôćĺ**Core query function and options:**
 67Ôćĺ
 68Ôćĺ```typescript
 69Ôćĺimport { query } from "@anthropic-ai/claude-agent-sdk";
 70Ôćĺ
 71Ôćĺinterface Options {
 72Ôćĺ  cwd?: string;
 73Ôćĺ  model?: string;
 74Ôćĺ  systemPrompt?: string | { type: 'preset'; preset: 'claude_code'; append?: string };
 75Ôćĺ  tools?: string[] | { type: 'preset'; preset: 'claude_code' };
 76Ôćĺ  allowedTools?: string[];
 77Ôćĺ  disallowedTools?: string[];
 78Ôćĺ  permissionMode?: 'default' | 'acceptEdits' | 'bypassPermissions' | 'plan';
 79Ôćĺ  maxTurns?: number;
 80Ôćĺ  maxBudgetUsd?: number;
 81Ôćĺ  outputFormat?: { type: 'json_schema', schema: JSONSchema };
 82Ôćĺ  mcpServers?: Record<string, McpServerConfig>;
 83Ôćĺ  hooks?: Partial<Record<HookEvent, HookCallbackMatcher[]>>;
 84Ôćĺ  sandbox?: SandboxSettings;
 85Ôćĺ  // ... 30+ additional options
 86Ôćĺ}
 87Ôćĺ```
 88Ôćĺ
 89Ôćĺ**Message types (SDK output):**
 90Ôćĺ
 91Ôćĺ```typescript
 92Ôćĺtype SDKMessage = SDKAssistantMessage | SDKUserMessage | SDKResultMessage | 
 93Ôćĺ                  SDKSystemMessage | SDKPartialAssistantMessage | SDKCompactBoundaryMessage;
 94Ôćĺ
 95Ôćĺtype SDKResultMessage = {
 96Ôćĺ  type: 'result';
 97Ôćĺ  subtype: 'success' | 'error_max_turns' | 'error_during_execution' | 
 98Ôćĺ           'error_max_budget_usd' | 'error_max_structured_output_retries';
 99Ôćĺ  uuid: UUID;
100Ôćĺ  session_id: string;
101Ôćĺ  duration_ms: number;
102Ôćĺ  duration_api_ms: number;
103Ôćĺ  is_error: boolean;
104Ôćĺ  num_turns: number;
105Ôćĺ  result?: string;
106Ôćĺ  total_cost_usd: number;
107Ôćĺ  usage: { input_tokens: number; output_tokens: number; /* ... */ };
108Ôćĺ  modelUsage: { [modelName: string]: ModelUsage };
109Ôćĺ  structured_output?: unknown;
110Ôćĺ  errors?: string[];
111Ôćĺ};
112Ôćĺ```
113Ôćĺ
114Ôćĺ**Built-in tool input types:**
115Ôćĺ
