140Ôćĺ## OpenCode provides a full OpenAPI specification
141Ôćĺ
142ÔćĺThe sst/opencode project is the **only CLI with a published OpenAPI 3.1.1 specification**, enabling automatic client generation. Types are auto-generated from the spec using `@hey-api/openapi-ts`.
