145Ôćĺ- **OpenAPI spec:** `packages/sdk/openapi.json` at https://github.com/sst/opencode/blob/dev/packages/sdk/openapi.json
146Ôćĺ- **Generated types:** `packages/sdk/js/src/gen/types.gen.ts`
147Ôćĺ- **npm packages:** `@opencode-ai/sdk` and `@opencode-ai/plugin`
